en: There's a villain in our waters! Help me deal with it.
An imperial frigate stood nearby. He ruins the whole business. Flood it! I won't be in debt!
Now I can sleep peacefully! Here is your reward. Do you take it?
Your boat has sunk... Steal a new ship?
You must be logged in to view the leaderboard
Now we can safely pass through the reefs. Want to go further?

Dangerous reefs ahead! Without a map
UI/NextLevel/EndGame,Congratulations on completing the game! Come join us in the next updates!
Tutorial/MoveTip,To swim press WASD
Tutorial/MoveTipMobile,To swim move your finger across the display
Tutorial/PirateBay,Hand over your loot and upgrade your ship in the bay
Tutorial/Attack,Booty! Swim closer! Your team will do everything themselves!
Tutorial/NextLevel,It's worth looking for a map from the locals...
Tutorial/HoldTip,Here you can hand over your loot
Tutorial/HealTip,Here you can patch up the ship
